latestIgtvVideos.caption:
With millions of luxury pieces awaiting to be rediscovered and reloved, scoring that covetable luxury handbag and other unique fashion finds is literally just a click away. Best of all, going through a verified second-hand reseller helps ensure that you get quality items with proven and genuine authenticity! Here's a few of my favorite picks from @labelcentric an Indian website showcasing pre loved accessories from leading brands from across the world!!

latestPosts.caption:
A big 👋 to everyone who's new to my page & a big thank you to each and every one of you who've been supporting me and pushing me to keep creating content over the last 3 years. Your encouragement means the world to me ❤️

Here are a few things about me 👇

☆ I'm a mom to twin teenagers and live in Chennai, India
☆ I'm 40 years old and truly believe in living my life to the fullest with no regrets. Because right now is the oldest you've ever been & the youngest you'll ever be again! 
☆ I'm the only Tam Bram in my family who's inclined towards fashion 😅 Studied microbiology & biochemistry only to be posting styling videos 20 years later!
☆ My love for fashion began when Nikita & I started @funkyfish.in in 2015 which eventually led to styling & blogging over the last 3 years. I'm so thankful to my community of women who've been so supportive & have been encouraging me ever since I started this fashion blog.
☆ Officially at an age where getting healthier & happier are my only two goals in life.
☆ Things that make me happy
- spending time with my closed one's
- a bottle or two of champagne 
- 70s or 80s english retro, melodic house & Ilayaraja songs
- curd rice with pickle 
☆ The one thing I'm most terrified of is flying ✈️ 
☆ I dont believe in following trends and feel what you wear should reflect your own personal style.
☆ I love collecting unique statement pieces of clothing, shoes & accessories irrespective of the brand or origin.

#allaboutme #stylemuze
